.SH SYNOPSIS
.sp
import example;
.SH DESCRIPTION
.sp
Example Varnish vmod demonstrating how to write an out\-of\-tree Varnish vmod
for Varnish 3.0.
.sp
Implements the traditional Hello World as a vmod.
